column16: Jacob deGrom pops out to second baseman Miguel Rojas.
Cody Hall intentionally walks Curtis Granderson.
Alejandro De Aza hits a ground-rule double (2) on a fly ball to right-center field.   Neil Walker scores.    Wilmer Flores scores.    Kevin Plawecki to 3rd.
Michael Conforto grounds out softly, second baseman Miguel Rojas to first baseman Chris Johnson.   Neil Walker to 3rd.    Wilmer Flores to 2nd.
James Loney pops out to shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria on the infield fly rule.
Wilmer Flores singles on a ground ball to left fielder Christian Yelich, deflected by shortstop Adeiny Hechavarria.   Neil Walker to 2nd.
Juan Lagares flies out to right fielder Giancarlo Stanton.
Rene Rivera homers (2) on a fly ball to left center field.   Wilmer Flores scores.
James Loney flies out to center fielder Marcell Ozuna.   Wilmer Flores to 3rd.
Wilmer Flores doubles (4) on a line drive to left fielder Christian Yelich.
Michael Conforto called out on strikes.
Neil Walker grounds out, second baseman Derek Dietrich to first baseman Justin Bour.
Yoenis Cespedes strikes out on a foul tip.
